The main reason we went to Old San Juan was to find a painting. This picture was taken on Monday when we walked all around San Juan looking for an art gallery. If you look to the left you will see a pink building behind the potted palm trees. Yup that is where we were trying to go. We walked every street but that one. We didn't find it until the next day after looking up art gallerys online.
